17 January 2021 Following the State of the Nation Address (SONA) delivered by President Ramaphosa on the 11th February 2021, the Government Communication and Information System (GCIS) is hosting a Youth Imbizo webinar. The purpose of the webinar is to create a platform for the youth to engage on the contents of the SONA and reflect on how it relates to them as the future of South Africa. The webinar will feature youth panellists from business, media and government. Members of the media are invited as follows:Date: Thursday, 18 February 2021Time: 10h00Platform: Zoom – (details to be shared with confirmed attendees) The webinar will also be streamed live on the SA Government Facebook page, Twitter and YouTube channels on the links below. Facebook: http://facebook.com/GovernmentZATwitter: http://twitter.com/GovernmentZAYouTube: https://www.youtube.com/user/GovernmentZA RSVP: Ishmael Selemale 072 637 7665 Email: Ishmael@gcis.gov.za Enquiries:Tshegofatso ModubuCell: 083 276 0786